<p class="ltx_p">We also suppose that <math id="S0.I2.i3.i2.p1.m4" class="ltx_Math" alttext="\mathbb{E}[T]&lt;\infty" display="inline"><mrow><mrow><mi>ğ”¼</mi><mo>â¢</mo><mrow><mo stretchy="false">[</mo><mi>T</mi><mo stretchy="false">]</mo></mrow></mrow><mo>&lt;</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">âˆ</mi></mrow></math>.
Show that <math id="S0.I2.i3.i2.p1.m5" class="ltx_Math" alttext="\mathbb{E}[X_{0}]\leq\mathbb{E}[X_{T}]&lt;\infty" display="inline"><mrow><mrow><mi>ğ”¼</mi><mo>â¢</mo><mrow><mo stretchy="false">[</mo><msub><mi>X</mi><mn>0</mn></msub><mo stretchy="false">]</mo></mrow></mrow><mo>â‰¤</mo><mrow><mi>ğ”¼</mi><mo>â¢</mo><mrow><mo stretchy="false">[</mo><msub><mi>X</mi><mi>T</mi></msub><mo stretchy="false">]</mo></mrow></mrow><mo>&lt;</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">âˆ</mi></mrow></math>.</p>
