<div class="ltx_proof">
<h6 class="ltx_title ltx_runin ltx_font_italic ltx_title_proof">Solution.</h6>
<div id="S0.I2.i3.i2.p2" class="ltx_para">
<p class="ltx_p"><math id="S0.I2.i3.i2.p2.m1" class="ltx_Math" alttext="X^{T}" display="inline"><msup><mi>X</mi><mi>T</mi></msup></math> is a submartingale for the same reason as before, and we
can again use dominated convergence if we find an integrable upper
bound. This upper bound is <math id="S0.I2.i3.i2.p2.m2" class="ltx_Math" alttext="TK+|X_{0}|" display="inline"><mrow><mrow><mi>T</mi><mo>â¢</mo><mi>K</mi></mrow><mo>+</mo><mrow><mo stretchy="false">|</mo><msub><mi>X</mi><mn>0</mn></msub><mo stretchy="false">|</mo></mrow></mrow></math> because</p>
<table id="S0.EGx9" class="ltx_equationgroup ltx_eqn_align ltx_eqn_table">

<tbody id="S0.Ex15"><tr class="ltx_equation ltx_eqn_row ltx_align_baseline">
<td class="ltx_eqn_cell ltx_eqn_center_padleft"></td>
<td class="ltx_td ltx_align_right ltx_eqn_cell"><math id="S0.Ex15.m1" class="ltx_Math" alttext="\displaystyle X^{T}_{n}" display="inline"><msubsup><mi>X</mi><mi>n</mi><mi>T</mi></msubsup></math></td>
<td class="ltx_td ltx_align_left ltx_eqn_cell"><math id="S0.Ex15.m2" class="ltx_Math" alttext="\displaystyle=X_{0}+\sum_{k=0}^{T\wedge n-1}X^{T}_{k+1}-X^{T}_{k}" display="inline"><mrow><mi></mi><mo>=</mo><mrow><mrow><msub><mi>X</mi><mn>0</mn></msub><mo>+</mo><mrow><mstyle displaystyle="true"><munderover><mo largeop="true" movablelimits="false" symmetric="true">âˆ‘</mo><mrow><mi>k</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn></mrow><mrow><mrow><mi>T</mi><mo>âˆ§</mo><mi>n</mi></mrow><mo>-</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></munderover></mstyle><msubsup><mi>X</mi><mrow><mi>k</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow><mi>T</mi></msubsup></mrow></mrow><mo>-</mo><msubsup><mi>X</mi><mi>k</mi><mi>T</mi></msubsup></mrow></mrow></math></td>
<td class="ltx_eqn_cell ltx_eqn_center_padright"></td></tr></tbody>
<tbody id="S0.Ex16"><tr class="ltx_equation ltx_eqn_row ltx_align_baseline">
<td class="ltx_eqn_cell ltx_eqn_center_padleft"></td>
<td class="ltx_td ltx_align_right ltx_eqn_cell"></td>
<td class="ltx_td ltx_align_left ltx_eqn_cell"><math id="S0.Ex16.m2" class="ltx_Math" alttext="\displaystyle\leq|X_{0}|+\sum_{k=0}^{T-1}K=|X_{0}|+TK.\qed" display="inline"><mrow><mrow><mi></mi><mo>â‰¤</mo><mrow><mrow><mo stretchy="false">|</mo><msub><mi>X</mi><mn>0</mn></msub><mo stretchy="false">|</mo></mrow><mo>+</mo><mrow><mstyle displaystyle="true"><munderover><mo largeop="true" movablelimits="false" symmetric="true">âˆ‘</mo><mrow><mi>k</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn></mrow><mrow><mi>T</mi><mo>-</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></munderover></mstyle><mi>K</mi></mrow></mrow><mo>=</mo><mrow><mrow><mo stretchy="false">|</mo><msub><mi>X</mi><mn>0</mn></msub><mo stretchy="false">|</mo></mrow><mo>+</mo><mrow><mi>T</mi><mo>â¢</mo><mi>K</mi></mrow></mrow></mrow><mo>.</mo><mo mathvariant="italic" separator="true">âˆ</mo></mrow></math></td>
